import "./order.css"; import Header from "../Components/Header/Header"; import Title from '../Components/Title/Title' import SummaryTable from './Components/Summary_table/table' import DetailTable from './Components/Detail_table/table' function Order(props) { return (
<div className="order-content"> <div className="order-detail"> <h2>Order Details</h2> <DetailTable /> </div> <div className="order-summary"> <h2>Order Summary</h2> <SummaryTable /> </div> <form action="" id="myfeedback"> <label for="myfeedback">MY FEEDBACK</label> <select name="rate" id="" form="carform"> <option value="volvo">Volvo</option> <option value="saab">Saab</option> <option value="opel">Opel</option> <option value="audi">Audi</option> </select> <input type="submit"/> </form> </div> </div> ); } export default Order;
